# Persona1 (Student)
## Catchy Name: Alfanso
### General Descritption: 
Had great time in college, partied a little too hard. Hit low point when he failed all his classes one semeter. Wants to turn his college carrer around

#### Frustrations:
- Wants to still party with friends but needs to spend time studying
- Peer pressure to have fun over school
- Having bad grades
- Cant find motivation to apply himself in school
- Doesnt have good study habits
- Needs to go to office hours / seek additional help 

#### Motivations:
- TURN LIFE AROUND!
- Get good grades
- Maintain friendships while not spending as much time with them
- Impress cute girl in math class with good test grades, convince her to join his study group
- Build good study habits
- balance social life, academic life, and gym 

#### Goals:
- Stop skipping class
- Participate in class discussions
- Ace next test
- Join academic organization
- Get the girl to go to dinner with him


#### Hobbies:
- working out
- partying
- skipping class
- pickup basketball
- collecting sports memes
- cars (BMW)

#### Unique characteristic:
- Traggic backstory, parents sacraficed everything to send him to college
- Has hidden motivation (extra pride)
- Grew up in a small town and never learned good study habits
- Secretly is an expert knitter/ sower (his mom always taught him)
- Spends his summers helping his father mine (his fathers health is bad and he doesnt want to lose his job)

# Persona2 (Non Student)


## Catchy Name: Doctor Rasta


### General Descritption: 
Grew up in the inner city of Oakland and visited Jamacia on a class trip in 9th grade. Recently graduated from Berkelee school of music and is currently a popular reggae artist. His parents inittialy did not support him but are now proud of what hes done. Despite his current succes, he is still ambitious and wants to have a #1 hit song.  


#### Frustrations:
- Has had 10 #2 hits but never a #1 hit
- People dont see reggae as a serious music genre
- He thinks his girlfrriend is cheating on him with a rock and roll artist
- Has hit a song writing slump
- Hes stressed about balding, which makes him bald even more

#### Motivations:
- spread love through music
- be the best reggae artist alive
- learn more instruments
- improve vocals, use less autotune
- have people all over the world know him / listen to his music

#### Goals:
- go on a world tour
- learn gutiar
- stalk his girlfriend until the truth is revealed
- make a #1 hit song
- stop his balding

#### Hobbies:
- making music
- natural herbs
- gardening
- bowling
- spending time with his pet ferett


#### Unique characteristic:
- has a ferett
- is very competitive
- oddly short
- has dreads... not for long
- has 2 different color eyes
